Genital system of 
<taxonomicName authority="Schilthuizen &amp; Clavera &amp; Khoo &amp; Bondar &amp; Elder &amp; Bouma &amp; Eddington &amp; Reisinger &amp; Cosentino &amp; Rossato &amp; Delledonne, 2019" authorityName="Schilthuizen &amp; Clavera &amp; Khoo &amp; Bondar &amp; Elder &amp; Bouma &amp; Eddington &amp; Reisinger &amp; Cosentino &amp; Rossato &amp; Delledonne" authorityYear="2019" box="[431,647,974,994]" class="Gastropoda" family="Ariophantidae" genus="Microparmarion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="3" pageNumber="38" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="exquadratus" status="n. sp.">
